<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">二话不说直接跳进粪池</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">将绳子套在猪的身上</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>经过半小时的努力</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>大家终于把这头猪拉了上来</strong><strong></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200913/46f224fd0571458ab4ef76d4bc92492a.gif" /></p>
